FrOSCon 11 - On August 20th and 21st we will meet again

This year there won't be any big changes. Therefore we just want to remind you 
on the two main changes from last year, which we will keep up:
* Free Entry
* Recruiting session

What is the FrOSCon?

Since 2004, every year more than 1,600 visitors come to FrOSCon - the Free and
Open Source Software Conference in St Augustin near Cologne. This makes FrOSCon
one of the biggest events of its kind in Germany. Present your company and
enrich our offer of talks, workshops and exhibition.

FrOSCon 2016 - When?

FrOSCon 2016 shall take place at the 20nd and 21st of August 2015 at the University
of Applied Sciences Bonn-Rhein-Sieg in Sankt Augustin.

Sponsoring - What is possible?

All information regarding the sponsoring can be found in the attached flyer. The 
design is new, the content not so much.

